summary: Graduated in electronic and instrumentation from Oran University , Mr HAMADOU Oussama is an control system engineer at oil & gas Company,. He manages DCS system, and PLC’s maintenance. He has 8 years experience in Honeywell TPS TDC 3000 System , instrument maintenance, calibration and loop tuning. He has also acquired experience in steam generator control, steam turbine control and anti-surge system
